bug.short_desc: [abrt] evince: cmsGetColorSpace(): evince-thumbnailer killed by SIGSEGV
bug.cf_doc_type: If docs needed, set a value

long_desc.thetext:
Version-Release number of selected component: evince-3.20.1-1.fc24
Additional info: reporter: libreport-2.7.2 backtrace_rating: 4 cmdline: evince-thumbnailer -s 128 file:///home/ericr/Downloads/Contacts%20-%20LightArrow%20Inc.pdf /home/ericr/.thumbnails/normal/2d51564244ec0bf8cb857d2344188adc.png crash_function: cmsGetColorSpace executable: /usr/bin/evince-thumbnailer global_pid: 4417 kernel: 4.6.4-301.fc24.x86_64 pkg_fingerprint: 73BD E983 81B4 6521 pkg_vendor: Fedora Project runlevel: N 5 type: CCpp uid: 1000
Truncated backtrace: Thread no. 1 (7 frames) #0 cmsGetColorSpace at cmsio0.c:934 #1 GfxICCBasedColorSpace::parse at GfxState.cc:2044 #2 GfxColorSpace::parse at GfxState.cc:406 #3 Page::loadThumb at Page.cc:689 #4 poppler_page_get_thumbnail at poppler-page.cc:491 #5 pdf_document_get_thumbnail at ev-poppler.cc:488 #6 evince_thumbnail_pngenc_get at evince-thumbnailer.c:182
Potential duplicate: bug 1293445
I've reported this to upstream at https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=97870. I'll wait whether he will accept my patch and will backport it then.
